{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "斑比 第4话 斑比的觉悟",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你说什么？用斑比的血\\n可以驾驭“深渊之种”？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110274_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝尔",
            "context": "不知道是不是真的可以……\\n不过至少帝国那帮人\\n是这么想的没错。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110362_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤里乌斯",
            "context": "单是深渊之种的话人类无法驾驭，\\n所以就以毒攻毒……\\n他们似乎是这个目的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110362_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤里乌斯",
            "context": "只要能驾驭深渊之种，\\n它就会成为无可比拟的强力武器。\\n毕竟我曾经尝试过，不会有错。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "就算是这样，也不能随便拿\\n女孩子的血对付滑溜溜的怪物啊。\\n真是失礼！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "说得对。而且如果目标是血，\\n最坏的情况是他们可能\\n都不会在意斑比的生死。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "在圣城的各位保护斑比的同时，\\n我们是不是赶紧\\n摧毁种子比较好？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110274_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝尔",
            "context": "没那么简单……\\n就在我们得到这个情报时，\\n那帮人突然就销声匿迹了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110274_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝尔",
            "context": "他们似乎是发现了\\n我们开始保护小姑娘，\\n所以起了戒备。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110274_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝尔",
            "context": "我们一路追踪他们的行迹，\\n感觉对方心态焦急，\\n不像是谨慎行事的货色。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110362_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤里乌斯",
            "context": "哼……也许是有什么人\\n从旁指点。总之，这样下去\\n我们是无法主动出击的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110274_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝尔",
            "context": "话虽如此，也不能放任\\n那种子在外。真让人头疼。\\n该怎么办才好……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "什么怎么办。\\n既然如此，斑比当诱饵\\n把他们引出来不就行了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "就算他们再怎么偷偷摸摸，\\n既然目标是斑比，\\n这就是最直接的方法。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "话是这么说……\\n不行，这太危险了。\\n简直是自投罗网。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "你又来了！\\n总是把斑比当小孩子！\\n听好了，斑比没问题的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "眷属你不是也亲眼看到\\n斑比收拾那头恶龙了吗！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "话虽如此……但不是说\\n那只是“真祖”的力量\\n一时觉醒而已吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "斑比现在的确使不出那种力量……\\n但是，只要斑比认真起来，\\n就是无敌的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔，但是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110362_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤里乌斯",
            "context": "她本人都说到这个份上了，\\n就让她试试如何？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "滑溜大叔！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110362_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤里乌斯",
            "context": "我们都知道她能够战斗。\\n而且我们其实也没余力\\n在这里停滞不前了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110362_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤里乌斯",
            "context": "虽然知道是往陷阱里跳，也只能\\n严阵以待把他们引过来。要是你甘愿\\n放任种子失控的话倒是另当别论。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我明白了……\\n不过，要好好拟定作战方案。\\n没问题吧？斑比。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "当然了！好……\\n就让你见识一下，\\n斑比想做就能做到！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "诱敌作战当天\\n街上",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那么……我们就按计划\\n在这附近候着，一有危险\\n你可要赶紧撤回来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "知道啦。只是用吸血鬼之力\\n把他们引出来而已，\\n没问题的，赶紧躲好吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "真是爱操心……\\n唉，赶紧搞定吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "教训一下那边的魔兽\\n就行了吧，看招！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "嘎呜！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "没人跳出来啊……\\n哼，没人的话\\n斑比可要回家了啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "这可不行啊。\\n我们再不抓住“真祖”，\\n可就没后路了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "不管用什么手段，\\n都要抓住“真祖”！\\n这可是那位大人的命令！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "坏蛋终于出现了！\\n不过，斑比可不会明知\\n你们要来还败下阵来！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "眷属，大叔们，上啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯！我在斑比身边保护她，\\n身后就拜托你们二位了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝尔",
            "context": "交给我们吧！\\n轰鸣吧——雷光！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "哼，护卫果然出现了啊，\\n不过无所谓！\\n把你们全部击溃就好！上！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵们",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110362_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤里乌斯",
            "context": "休想。哼！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "没用的！\\n你以为赢得了这么多人吗！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110362_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤里乌斯",
            "context": "呃……\\n人果然比上次更多了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110274_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝尔",
            "context": "是啊，不过赌上雷迅卿骑士团之名，\\n决不会屈服于这点人！哈啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110362_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤里乌斯",
            "context": "真要命。那我也稍微\\n拿出点真本事吧——亡灵触手！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵们",
            "context": "唔啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "诶～厉害！雷电大叔\\n和滑溜大叔都很厉害嘛！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯，别松懈，我们也出手吧！\\n烈焰王冠！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "好！看招，\\n尝尝斑比的厉害！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "唔唔唔唔唔唔！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "哼哼，\\n简直小菜一碟！\\n好了，乖乖投降吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "唔……\\n吸血鬼的力量果然不是盖的……\\n那就只能豁出去了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "诶？\\n大叔你要做什么……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "“深渊之种”啊！\\n我这条命就给你了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "现在就释放你的力量！\\n然后吞噬真祖，\\n变得更加强大吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "法尔艾斯大人！\\n望明鉴我的决心！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "呀啊啊！？什、什么！？\\n发生什么了！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110362_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤里乌斯",
            "context": "不好，“深渊之种”要被释放了！\\n那东西一旦觉醒就会立刻吞噬\\n周围的生命体，重新开始活动！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110274_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝尔",
            "context": "而使用者则会被种子吞噬\\n并丧失心智，不分敌我展开攻击。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "深渊之种",
            "context": "咕呜呜……咕嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "噫、噫噫！？\\n为、为什么朝我们来了！？\\n住手，快住手啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "不要，我不想死！\\n不要吃我，不要啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "不好！那个敌人大叔\\n身上也长出了什么东西！\\n赶紧想想办法啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110362_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤里乌斯",
            "context": "我知道。要尽快摧毁种子，\\n把它从宿主身上剥离！但是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110274_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝尔",
            "context": "种子不断吞噬那些士兵，\\n其力量正以惊人的速度增长！\\n可恶，攻击都……够不着！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "深渊之种",
            "context": "咕嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不好，那边吞噬得差不多了\\n就冲我们这边来了！\\n目标是——呃，是我吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110274_01",
                "110362_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝尔",
            "context": "尤蒂尔！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110362_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤里乌斯",
            "context": "王子！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "休想得逞！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斑比",
            "context": "呀啊！\\n呜呜！好疼……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110388_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "斑比！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "深渊之种",
            "context": "血……真祖之血！\\n唔嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110274_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔贝尔",
            "context": "唔，该死的深渊之种\\n好像吸收了小姑娘流的血！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110362_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤里乌斯",
            "context": "能感觉到它的力量膨胀了……\\n才吸了几滴就这样，\\n真祖之血着实可怕。",
            "voice_line": "",
